      <title>聯準會威廉斯表示聯準會下一步可能是降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-williams-says-next-fed-move-likely-be-lower-rates-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紐約聯邦儲備銀行行長約翰威廉斯週一表示，聯準會將在某個不確定的時刻降低利率目標。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-williams-says-next-fed-move-likely-be-lower-rates-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 18:12:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>聯準會巴爾金：當前利率水準將抑制需求，不會出現“過熱”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-barkin-current-rate-level-will-cool-demand-doesnt-see-overheating-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士滿聯儲主席托馬斯·巴爾金(Thomas Barkin)週一表示，聯準會目前的基準利率水準應該足以讓經濟降溫，從而使通膨率回到央行2%的目標，而就業市場的強勁讓官員們有時間等待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-barkin-current-rate-level-will-cool-demand-doesnt-see-overheating-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 17:08:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
